# Architecture

- **Domain** (`SeedWork\Domain\*`): Entity, ValueObject, AggregateRoot, DomainEvent, EntityId, EventId, Repository, UnitOfWork, AggregateObtainer, DomainException / ValueException / NotFoundResource.
- **Application** (`SeedWork\Application\*`): Command, CommandBus, CommandHandler, Query, QueryBus, QueryHandler, QueryResult, DomainEventBus, DomainEventHandler.
- **Infrastructure** (`SeedWork\Infrastructure\*`): ContainerCommandBus, ContainerQueryBus, TransactionalCommandBus, DeferredDomainEventBus, DomainEventFlushCommandBus.

See [docs/component-reference.md](../../docs/component-reference.md) for every interface and base class.
